footnote-anchor-1" href="#footnote-1" target="_self">1</a> that keeps the brain deliciously addicted.</p><p>A surreal &#8216;omg Senpai noticed me&#8217; moment was when I heard a big tech product group had read the piece and was contemplating implementing some of XHS&#8217;s features. Stay tuned for whether some of the features mentioned get into a consumer tech offering near you.</p><p><em>The most thought-provoking piece:</em> <strong>The Chinese Tech Playbook for Winning - Part I</strong></p><div class="embedded-post-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:48603102,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://lillianli.substack.com/p/the-chinese-tech-playbook-for-winning&quot;,&quot;publication_id&quot;:80709,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Chinese Characteristics&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e34121c4-fa15-41d2-bea1-69182c1fc07a_1125x1125.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Chinese Tech Playbook for Winning - Part I&quot;,&quot;truncated_body_text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2022-02-11T17:15:50.854Z&quot;,&quot;like_count&quot;:19,&quot;comment_count&quot;:0,&quot;bylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:3249443,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Lillian Li&quot;,&quot;previous_name&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/20b913eb-e477-43cb-a0dd-9c26ec0b8698_1088x728.png&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Refactoring. Private company investment @ Baillie Gifford. Prev - Eight Roads Ventures, Salesforce Ventures, LEK Consulting. Cambridge and LSE alum. \n@lillianmli\n&quot;,&quot;profile_set_up_at&quot;:&quot;2021-07-16T08:12:18.387Z&quot;,&quot;publicationUsers&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:90983,&quot;user_id&quot;:3249443,&quot;publication_id&quot;:80709,&quot;role&quot;:&quot;admin&quot;,&quot;public&quot;:true,&quot;is_primary&quot;:false,&quot;publication&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:80709,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Chine