#183; 19 likes &#183; Lillian Li</div></a></div><p>These days, I gravitate more towards operators for new <a href="https://lillianli.substack.com/p/the-mental-models-of-chinese-tech">mental models</a>. Their hard-won wisdom results from unique vantage points battle-tested by reality. A stand-out collection of insights came from the Tsinghua university lecture notes of Wang Huiwen (Meituan&#8217;s co-founder who retired as a billionaire in his forties) on product development. Wang&#8217;s teachings, remixed and synthesised here by yours truly, were revelational in terms of having a cohesive framework for finding and developing the next big consumer thing.</p><p><em>The most</em> <em>influential piece for the future:</em> <strong>Internet and the murmurs of post-modernity in China</strong></p><div class="embedded-post-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:53032304,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://lillianli.substack.com/p/internet-and-the-murmurs-of-post&quot;,&quot;publication_id&quot;:80709,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Chinese Characteristics&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e34121c4-fa15-41d2-bea1-69182c1fc07a_1125x1125.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Internet and the murmurs of post-modernity in China&quot;,&quot;truncated_body_text&quot;:null,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2022-04-28T15:00:42.084Z&quot;,&quot;like_count&quot;:13,&quot;comment_count&quot;:1,&quot;bylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:3249443,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Lillian Li&quot;,&quot;previous_name&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/20b913eb-e477-43cb-a0dd-9c26ec0b8698_1088x728.png&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Refactoring. Private company investment @ Baillie Gifford. Prev - Eight Roads Ventures, Salesforce Ventures, LEK Consulting. Cambridge and LSE alum. \n@lillianmli\n&quot;,&quot;profile_set_up_at&quot;:&quot;2021-07-16T08